sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant UI as UI
  participant K as Kong
  participant AI as AI Service
  participant S3 as S3
  participant SQL as SQL
  participant W as Parse Worker

  U->>UI: Upload resume
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/documents/upload-url JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>SQL: doc row PENDING
  AI-->>UI: presigned URL + documentId
  UI->>S3: PUT PDF file

  AI->>W: queue parse
  W->>S3: GET file
  W->>SQL: READY + JSON

  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/documents/id JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>SQL: read status JSON
  AI-->>UI: parsed resume JSON
